<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Advanced AI Outbound</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      header {
        background-color: #0056b3;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .intro {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      .intro p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .intro ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .intro ul li {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        background-color: #0073e6;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #005bb5;
      }
      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 0;
        background-color: #0056b3;
        color: white;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Welcome to Advanced AI Outbound</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
      <section class="intro">
        <p>Advanced AI Outbound tool:</p>
        <p>
          Advanced AI Outbound automatically finds job openings on LinkedIn,
          gets contact info, and sends personalized emails to help companies
          fill positions.
        </p>
        <p>Here's a step-by-step breakdown of the process:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Identify job opportunities on LinkedIn</li>
          <li>Find relevant personas through Apollo</li>
          <li>Enrich their emails (i.e., gather email addresses)</li>
          <li>
            Send personalized outreach emails stating, "I saw you are hiring for
            ABCD job and we can help."
          </li>
          <li>Use this tool to differentiate and grow revenue</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <a href="/find-jobs" class="cta-button">Find Jobs</a>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Advanced AI Outbound. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
